    <item>
      <title>许多人都希望看到抵押贷款利率下降：斯珀林</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/many-would-love-to-see-mortgage-rates-go-down-sperling-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫高级顾问吉恩·斯珀林表示，许多人都希望看到抵押贷款减少，但创纪录的小企业申请则表明人们对经济充满信心。他在“彭博市场”节目中与索纳莉·巴萨克进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/many-would-love-to-see-mortgage-rates-go-down-sperling-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 18:05:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷准备在投资领域实现“多次”退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/carlyle-ready-to-make-a-number-of-exits-in-investments-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团美洲企业私募股权联席主管 Brian Bernasek 表示，随着私募股权交易市场反弹，凯雷集团正准备退出“大量”投资。他表示，强劲的信贷市场和稳定的利率是部分原因。他接受了彭博社 Sonali Basak 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/carlyle-ready-to-make-a-number-of-exits-in-investments-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 18:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
