    <item>
      <title>非洲的多元选择面临多重阻力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/africa-s-multichoice-faces-multiple-headwinds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲最大的流媒体公司在公布财年收益时面临多重阻力，例如宏观经济环境疲软以及尼日利亚奈拉大幅贬值。彭博新闻社的 Jennifer Zabasajja 与 Joumanna Bercetche 在 Horizo​​ns Middle East &amp; Africa 上讨论了这些挑战。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/africa-s-multichoice-faces-multiple-headwinds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:47:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stifel 关闭卡尔加里办事处，削减多伦多银行家职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/stifel-shuts-calgary-office-cuts-investment-bank-jobs-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯蒂费尔金融公司 (Stifel Financial Corp.) 关闭了其卡尔加里办事处，结束了加拿大石油行业能源投资银行业务的辉煌，同时还解雇了多伦多的一些投资银行家和分析师。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/stifel-shuts-calgary-office-cuts-investment-bank-jobs-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:47:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
